column1: Baby Barnaby's////Disappointing first time visit. Was Saturday 10am
column3: no problem. Waited on and ordered. Later
column4: a couple sat next to us and the man ordered same meal as me. We waited 45 min for ch fried steak/eggs. That couple got served
column5: ate and finished before we even got our food. Had to complain by then. Food came at 11. Steak was ok
column6: eggs were runny and undercooked. Wanted breakfast
